	dprr:hasNoteText "He issued coins in 49 in Spain inscribed Varro Proq. Magn. Procos. See MRR 2.100, note 7, and now Crawford, RRC 1.463, no. 447. To be distinguished from M. Terentius Varro, whose title was Legatus pro praetore.\n" .
